bio roots really come in handy.

626
00:24:50,990 --> 00:24:53,230
The prodromal phase is
the initial symptoms

627
00:24:53,230 --> 00:24:58,000
of exposure, which may or may
not happen one to three days

628
00:24:58,000 --> 00:24:59,410
after exposure.

629
00:24:59,410 --> 00:25:01,588
For massive exposure,
you're not going

630
00:25:01,588 --> 00:25:03,130
to see this, because
you're not going

631
00:25:03,130 --> 00:25:05,020
to live one to three days.

632
00:25:05,020 --> 00:25:07,420
For very minor exposure,
you may not even

633
00:25:07,420 --> 00:25:12,880
see these prodromal effects,
like a drop in blood cell

634
00:25:12,880 --> 00:25:15,550
count, or GI syndrome,
because the dose might not

635
00:25:15,550 --> 00:25:19,300
be severe enough for your body
not to be able to cope with it.

636
00:25:19,300 --> 00:25:21,190
The latent phase this,
is the tricky one.

637
00:25:21,190 --> 00:25:24,790
An apparent recovery from
the prodromal systems.

638
00:25:24,790 --> 00:25:26,950
So getting a medium dose
of radiation-- let's call,

639
00:25:26,950 --> 00:25:28,720
that like 2 to 5 gray--

640
00:25:28,720 --> 00:25:31,320
will cause some nausea,
vomiting, and headache.

641
00:25:31,320 --> 00:25:33,150
And then you get better.

642
00:25:33,150 --> 00:25:37,390
And then you get worse in
the manifest illness phase,

643
00:25:37,390 --> 00:25:39,730
because a lot of the things
that radiation will do

644
00:25:39,730 --> 00:25:41,410
can be immediate.

645
00:25:41,410 --> 00:25:45,520
If you suddenly cause the
body to release serotonin

646
00:25:45,520 --> 00:25:47,770
and induce the
vomiting reflex, that

647
00:25:47,770 --> 00:25:50,455
goes away once that serotonin
is consumed or dealt with.

648
00:25:50,455 --> 00:25:52,330
