1180
00:48:33,730 --> 00:48:36,520
you could irradiate single
cells and watch what

1181
00:48:36,520 --> 00:48:38,260
happens to the cells nearby.

1182
00:48:38,260 --> 00:48:41,150
So to study in a controlled
